lead_paragraph: The prosecutor’s office said it had detained a new suspect and released one who had been detained, though the man who was released will be required to appear before a judge.
snippet: The prosecutor’s office said it had detained a new suspect and released one who had been detained, though the man who was released will be required to appear before a judge.

headline.main: New Suspect in Paris Attacks Is Detained, Belgian Officials Say
headline.print_headline: New Suspect in Paris Attacks Is Detained by Belgians

abstract: Belgian prosecutor's office announces it has detained Zakaria J, new suspect in Paris terrorist attacks, and has released another who had been previously detained; announcement brings total of people detained in connection with attacks in Belgium to nine people.
